                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/flowermumu/">欢乐分裂</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-11-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">草木茶食中显人生，见微知著，用笔极为克制，鲜有表达自己主观态度，以考据为主；疏淡文字仍洋溢着浓浓八卦味，有极高艺术天分的天才们往往也拥有并不明亮的一面。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="566358868">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-566358868" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-566358868" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="566358868">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ligne/">黎戈</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-09-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">含蓄韬晦，有营养的书，低调实力派</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="607609482">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-607609482" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-607609482" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="607609482">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chengzhimo/">成知默</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-11-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">花事、人事、书事、茶事、食事，事事洞明，文字信息密度高，八卦摭拾读来也颇有趣味。所引小津在母亲逝世后所写日记：“春天在晴空下盛放，樱花开得灿烂。一个人留在这里，我只感到茫然，想起秋刀鱼之味。残落的樱花有如布碎，清酒带着黄连的苦味”，颇有其影片清简静穆之味。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="616206607">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-616206607" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-616206607" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="616206607">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lilyshen/">玑衡</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">为什么这么一本讲风物的书，却没有配任何能帮助了解文字的图片呢……文字是不错的，但是似乎作者过于喜爱冈仓天心了。如果对这个冈仓不了解的话，那书里有三四篇文章都会觉得懵懵懂懂。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="582118450">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-582118450" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-582118450" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="582118450">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/esotericmc/">le frisson™</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-10-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">好的散文能燃起好奇心和求知欲，教人想去探访更宏大的世界之间精微的关联。谢谢澜老师的馈赠！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

